com.forst.lukas.pibe.data

Class PibeConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.forst.lukas.pibe.data.PibeConfiguration

  • public class PibeConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    Whole configuration of application is stored here. Class is full of getters and setters.
    If is WiFi enabled, sending enabled etc. and whether has application access to the:
    • Manifest.permission#READ_PHONE_STATE
    • Manifest.permission#READ_CONTACTS
    • Manifest.permission#CAMERA
    • Manifest.permission#BIND_NOTIFICATION_LISTENER_SERVICE

    Data is stored here as well:
    • ipAddress - String of IP Address of the server
    • port - Port of the server
    • installedAppsNames - list of the installed applications names
    • filteredApps - applications which are filtered
    • lastUsedIPsAndPorts - HashMap with history of used IPs and ports
    Author:
    Lukas Forst
